commit.message:
freebsd.h (ENDFILE_SPEC): Add space to separate object files.

2006-02-02  Andreas Tobler  <a.tobler@schweiz.ch>

	* config/sparc/freebsd.h (ENDFILE_SPEC): Add space to separate
	object files.

From-SVN: r110520
